snippet.title: I Expect You To Die Seat of Power Trailer
snippet.description:
Outwit Dr. Zor by sneaking into a private Zoraxis boardroom and securing top secret information. 

This new level will be available for free on July 16, 2019, on all currently supported VR platforms.

'I Expect You To Die' is a virtual reality (VR) puzzle game that places you in the well-polished shoes of an elite secret agent. You must attempt to survive deadly situations in immersive and dangerous locales. 

'I Expect You To Die' is available now on Oculus Rift, HTC Vive, PlayStation®VR, and Windows Mixed Reality.

Buy the Game:
▸ Windows Mixed Reality: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/i-expect-you-to-die/9pldjkk7dnvm?activetab=pivot:overviewtab
▸ Oculus: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1115950031749190/
▸ HTC Vive: http://store.steampowered.com/app/587430/I_Expect_You_To_Die/
▸ PS VR: https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/i-expect-you-to-die/cid=UP0937-CUSA05590_00-IEYTD00000000001

Stay informed:
▸ Website: https://iexpectyoutodie.schellgames.com/
▸ Discord: http://discord.gg/ATgr6BbHdt
▸ Twitter: https://twitter.com/ieytd
▸ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ieytd/
